---
title: Speedy Bacon, Mushroom & Cheese Spaghetti with Toasted Almonds & Pear Salad
description: There’s a lot to love about this rich pasta dish, from the savoury bacon to the melted Parmesan cheese and deep meatiness of the mushrooms. But our favourite part? It’s got to be that it’s on the table in half an hour. That’s our kind of dinner!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/cheese-bacon-fusilli-20720db1.jpg
